<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/8722> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #8722" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/7> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "p. 751, footnote 371" ;
	dprr:hasID 8722 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4552> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4552" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Propraetor in Sicily (see 73, Promagistrates). On his mistreatment, perhaps in this year, his last in Sicily, of Sertorian refugees, see Cic. Verr. 2.5.72 and 146 and 151-155; cf. Oros. 6.3.5." ;
	dprr:hasID 4552 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4512> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4512" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Propraetor in Sicily (see 73, Promagistrates). Cf. Cic. Verr. 2.2.4, and 5.5; Sall. Hist. 4.32 M; cf. Plut. Crass. 10.3." ;
	dprr:hasID 4512 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4471> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4471" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Propraetor in Sicily (praetor, Cic. Verr. 2.2.11, and passim; praetura, Verr. 2.2.17, and passim; praetorium imperium, Verr. 2.5.40). He governed Sicily for three years, his expected successor Q. Arrius being appointed to the war against Spartacus (Cic. Verr. 2.2.37, and 4.42; Div. in Caec. 3 and 11). On his crimes and misgovernment, and his trial and condemnation in 70, see Cic. Verr. passim, and the Scholia on these, ed. Stangl; Ascon. 17 C; Sall. Hist. 4.32, and 53 M; Plut. Cic. 7-8." ;
	dprr:hasID 4471 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4411> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4411" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Cic. Verr. 2.1.102-158 passim; 2.1.34, and 5.34; Cluent. 91; Ps.-Ascon. 216, 255, and 257 Stangl." ;
	dprr:hasID 4411 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4279> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4279" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Legatus pro quaestore under Dolabella in Cilicia (see 80, Legates)." ;
	dprr:hasID 4279 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4253> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4253" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Legate, then Legatus pro quaestore, under Cn. Dolabella in Cilicia (Cic. Verr. 1.11; 2.1.41-102; Ps.-Ascon. 194- 245 Stangl, passim; Schol. Gron. 324-348 Stangl, passim)." ;
	dprr:hasID 4253 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4168> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4168" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Probably still a Proquaestor (Cic. Verr. 2.1.34-40; see 83-81, Promagistrates)." ;
	dprr:hasID 4168 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4129> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4129" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Continued, now probably Proquaestor, under the Consul Papirius in Gaul, and then deserted him for Sulla (Cic. Verr. 2.1.34-40, and 3.177; Ps.-Ascon. 208 Stangl)." ;
	dprr:hasID 4129 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4103> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4103" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Assigned to serve under the Consul Papirius Carbo in Picenum (Cic. Verr. 2.1.11 and 34-40, and 3.177; Ps.- Ascon. 206, 208, 226 Stangl; Schol. Gron. 329, 332f. Stangl)." ;
	dprr:hasID 4103 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4102> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4102" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "3 Bülz, De Prov. Rom. Quaest. (Diss. Leipzig, 1893) 55, and Lübker, Lex.8, date the quaestorship of Verres in 82, Carbo's third consulship; but Cicero quite clearly dates it 14 years before the trial and one year before the consulship of Scipio in 83." ;
	dprr:hasID 4102 .
